OL,3,CTribute to BMX rider 'loved beyond
OL,4,Cwords' after fatal crash
OL,6,FThe family of a cyclist killed
OL,7,Ffollowing a road accident in
OL,8,FWaterlooville, have paid tribute to
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,F31-year-old Lee Joshua Grant died on
OL,12,FThursday 16 July, two days after his
OL,13,Fbike collided with a car on College
OL,14,FRoad.
OL,16,FPolice were called to the scene at
OL,17,F10.41am on Tuesday, where Lee had
OL,18,Fsuffered serious injuries and was
OL,19,Frushed to hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
