PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784623688
OL,3,CTribute to BMX rider 'loved beyond
OL,4,Cwords' after fatal crash
OL,6,FToday his mother said: "Lee was loved
OL,7,Fbeyond words and his loss has left a
OL,8,Fhole in the hearts of everyone who
OL,9,Fknew him.
OL,11,F"Lee had a passion for BMX riding and
OL,12,Fa very cheeky smile that would
OL,13,Fbrighten anyone's day, with a kind
OL,14,Fheart to match. He cared deeply for
OL,15,Fothers and was always willing to help
OL,16,Fanyone, never expecting anything in
OL,17,Freturn. His kindness and generosity
OL,18,Ftouched the lives of so many people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1784623688
OL,3,CTribute to BMX rider 'loved beyond
OL,4,Cwords' after fatal crash
OL,6,F"Even in death, my boy continued to
OL,7,Fhelp others. As an organ donor, he has
OL,8,Fgiven the gift of life to others,
OL,9,Fsomething that makes me incredibly
OL,10,Fproud.
OL,12,F"I want to thank everyone who worked
OL,13,Fto help Lee at the scene that day and
OL,14,Fin the days that followed, as well as
OL,15,Fall those who supported Lee and our
OL,16,Ffamily during the most difficult time
OL,17,Fof our lives.
OL,19,F"Lee will never be forgotten. I will
OL,20,Fcarry him in my heart forever and
OL,21,Ftreasure every memory we shared."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
